<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light" />
    <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light" />
    <title>Verificação de Segurança • {{#if brandName}}{{brandName}}{{else}}Turbofy{{/if}}</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#f5f7fb; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif; color:#0f172a;">
    <!-- Preheader (hidden) -->
    <div style="display:none; max-height:0; overflow:hidden; opacity:0;">
      {{#if preheader}}{{preheader}}{{else}}Seu código de verificação para acessar o Dashboard{{/if}}
    </div>

    <!-- Wrapper -->
    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background:#f5f7fb;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 24px 12px;">
          <!-- Card -->
          <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width:600px; background:#ffffff; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08); overflow:hidden;">
            <!-- Header Brand -->
            <tr>
              <td style="background:#0b1220; padding:24px; text-align:center;">
                {{#if logoUrl}}
                  <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="{{#if brandName}}{{brandName}}{{else}}Turbofy{{/if}}" width="128" style="border:0; outline:none; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;" />
                {{else}}
                  <div style="font-weight:800; font-size:24px; letter-spacing:0.5px; color:#ffffff;">
                    {{#if brandName}}{{brandName}}{{else}}Turbofy{{/if}}
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#cbd5e1; margin-top:6px;">Gateway de Pagamentos</div>
                {{/if}}
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Body -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:28px 28px 8px;">
                <div style="font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#0f172a;">Autenticação de Dois Fatores</div>
                <div style="font-size:14px; color:#334155; margin-top:8px; line-height:1.6;">
                  Use o código abaixo para concluir sua verificação de segurança e acessar seu Dashboard.
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- OTP Code -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:8px 28px 20px;">
                <div style="background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:12px; padding:18px; text-align:center;">
                  <div style="font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, Monaco, monospace; font-size:32px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:6px; color:#0f172a;">
                    {{code}}
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:12px; color:#64748b; margin-top:8px;">Este código expira em 5 minutos.</div>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- CTA Button -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:4px 28px 8px; text-align:center;">
                <a href="{{#if actionUrl}}{{actionUrl}}{{else}}https://turbofy.com{{/if}}" style="display:inline-block; background:#2563eb; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; padding:12px 20px; border-radius:10px; font-weight:700; font-size:14px;">
                  Verificar agora
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Notes -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:12px 28px 0;">
                <div style="font-size:12px; color:#334155; line-height:1.6;">
                  • Se você não solicitou este código, ignore este e-mail.<br/>
                  • Por segurança, nunca compartilhe seu código. Nossa equipe jamais solicitará este código por telefone ou chat.
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Divider -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:18px 28px 0;">
                <div style="height:1px; background:#e2e8f0; width:100%;"></div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Support -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:16px 28px 24px;">
                <div style="font-size:12px; color:#475569;">
                  Precisa de ajuda? Fale com nosso suporte:
                  <a href="mailto:{{#if supportEmail}}{{supportEmail}}{{else}}suporte@turbofy.com{{/if}}" style="color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;">
                    {{#if supportEmail}}{{supportEmail}}{{else}}suporte@turbofy.com{{/if}}
                  </a>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td style="background:#0b1220; padding:18px 24px; text-align:center;">
                <div style="font-size:12px; color:#cbd5e1;">
                  © {{#if year}}{{year}}{{else}}2025{{/if}} {{#if brandName}}{{brandName}}{{else}}Turbofy{{/if}} • Pagamentos com segurança, performance e conformidade.
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
  
</html>